result.execSummary:
The defendant Dustin C Geissler was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Dustin C Geissler is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Dustin C Geissler was found guilty of Battery, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
  • Dustin C Geissler was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct, a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
